data.description: Located in the Desert Lakes Golf Community, this 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is situated on a nice corner lot that backs up to the golf course. There are two separate fenced patios - one with a 220V that is ready for a hot tub - and a deck off the upstairs primary bedroom that overlooks the golf course. A double-sided fireplace keeps the primary bedroom AND bathroom cozy and warm! Home is priced to sell and is being sold as-is! Schedule an appointment today! Solar was just installed this year so low energy bills await the new owners! The living room and back patio are wired with surround sound speakers, perfect for entertainment. The exterior trim was recently painted and the current owner has had pest control services every 3 months since occupancy, so pest issues are highly unlikely.
